  "title": "TripletMarginLoss-API Document-PaddlePaddle Deep Learning Platform",
  "description": "Creates a criterion that measures the triplet loss given an input tensors\\(x1\\),\\(x2\\),\\(x3\\)and a margin with a value greater than\\(0\\). This is used for measuring a relative similarity between samples. A triplet is composed byinput,positiveandnegative(i.e.,input,positive examplesandnegative examplesrespectively). The shapes of all input tensors should be\\((N, *)\\).",
  "parameters": [
